#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbreakout; is a Breakout-like game."
msgstr "&kbreakout; je igra podobna igrici Breakout."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbreakout; gameboard"
msgstr "&kbreakout; igralna plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The object of the game is to destroy as many bricks as possible without "
"losing the ball."
msgstr "Cilj igre je uničiti čim več opek brez izgube žoge."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player is presented with a game field containing a number of bricks. A "
"ball travels across the screen, bouncing off the top and side walls. When a "
"brick is hit, the ball bounces away and the brick is destroyed. The player "
"loses a life when the ball touches the bottom of the field. To prevent this "
"from happening, the player has to use a movable bar to bounce the ball "
"upward, situated at the bottom of the window. The purpose of the game is to "
"progress through the levels destroying all bricks present in each, and "
"trying to get a highscore."
msgstr ""
"Pred igralcem je igralno polje, ki vsebuje več kock. Žoga potuje po zaslonu "
"in se odbija od zgornje in stranske stene. Ko je opeka udarjena, se žogica "
"odbije in opeka je uničena. Igralec izgubi življenje, ko se žoga dotakne dna "
"igrišča. Da se to ne bi zgodilo, mora igralec uporabiti premično palico za "
"odbijanje žogice navzgor, ki se nahaja na dnu okna. Namen igre je "
"napredovati skozi ravni, uničiti vse opeke, ki so v vsaki, in poskušati "
"doseči najboljši rezultat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some bricks have a special behavior, or may let a gift fall down when hit. "
"The gifts can be caught with the bar, their behavior can be either positive "
"or negative. For further information on the different types of bricks and "
"gifts see the next chapter."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere opeke se obnašajo na poseben način ali pa lahko ob udarcu podarjeno "
"padejo dol. Darila je mogoče ujeti s palico, njihovo obnašanje je lahko "
"pozitivno ali negativno. Za nadaljnje informacije o različnih vrstah opek in "
"daril glejte naslednje poglavje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To fire the ball press the spacebar, to move the bar use the mouse or the "
"arrow keys. The ball will bounce in the direction of the side of the bar it "
"bounced on hit, the more it bounces near the left end of the bar the more it "
"will bounce toward the left, the same applies for the right side; if it "
"bounces in the middle of the bar it will bounce straight toward the top."
msgstr ""
"Za izstrelitev žogice pritisnite preslednico, za premikanje palice uporabite "
"miško ali puščične tipke. Žoga se bo odbila v smeri strani palice, od katere "
"se je odbila ob udarcu, bolj ko se bo odbila blizu levega konca palice, bolj "
"se bo odbila proti levi, enako velja za desno stran; če odskoči na sredini "
"palice, bo odskočila naravnost proti vrhu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable the option <guilabel>Fire on mouse click</guilabel> in the "
"settings dialog, you can click with the &LMB; to fire. Enabling the option "
"will make the game steal the mouse cursor, pause the game to get the cursor "
"back."
msgstr ""
"Če v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami omogočite možnost <guilabel>Proži ob "
"kliku miške</guilabel>, lahko kliknete z &LMB; za strel. Če omogočite "
"možnost, bo igra ukradla kazalec miške, začasno ustavite igro, da vrnete "
"kazalec nazaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Passing a level awards 300 points to the player. A level is passed when all "
"breakable and visible bricks are destroyed, or alternatively if the next "
"level gift is caught. In the latter case an additional score for each "
"remaining brick is awarded."
msgstr ""
"Prehod nivoja igralcu podeli 300 točk. Raven je opravljena, ko so uničene "
"vse lomljive in vidne opeke ali če je ujeto darilo naslednje stopnje. V "
"slednjem primeru se dodeli dodatna točka za vsako preostalo opeko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A score is awarded for every brick destroyed, the smaller the interval "
"between one hit and the following the higher this score."
msgstr ""
"Točka se dodeli za vsako uničeno opeko, manjši kot je interval med enim "
"zadetkom in naslednjim, višji je ta rezultat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The gifts hidden in a given level are fixed, their position however is "
"random."
msgstr ""
"Darila, skrita v dani ravni, so fiksna, njihov položaj pa je naključen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "30 points are awarded for every gift caught."
msgstr "Za vsako ulovljeno darilo prejmete 30 točk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player loses a life when the ball touches the bottom of the field and "
"there are no other balls left in the game, or when the player catches a lose "
"life gift. When losing a life, 1000 points are detracted from his score."
msgstr ""
"Igralec izgubi življenje, ko se žoga dotakne dna polja in v igri ni nobene "
"druge žoge ali ko igralec ujame darilo za izgubljeno življenje. Ko izgubi "
"življenje, se njegovemu rezultatu odvzame 1000 točk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional lives can be gained by catching the add life gifts."
msgstr ""
"Dodatna življenja je mogoče pridobiti z lovljenjem dodanih življenjskih "
"daril."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game ends when the player loses the ball while not having any additional "
"lives left, or when all levels have been won."
msgstr ""
"Igra se konča, ko igralec izgubi žogo, medtem ko nima več življenj ali ko so "
"osvojene vse stopnje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brick Types"
msgstr "Vrste opeke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pictures for the bricks below are for the default theme of &kbreakout;."
msgstr "Slike za spodnje kocke so za privzeto temo &kbreakout;."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plain Brick"
msgstr "Navadna opeka"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plain Bricks"
msgstr "Navadne opeke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simple bricks, while their appearance may vary they all behave the same way, "
"they get destroyed when hit by the ball and may contain a gift."
msgstr ""
"Preproste opeke, čeprav se njihov videz lahko razlikuje, se vse obnašajo "
"enako, uničijo se, ko jih udari žogica, in lahko vsebujejo darilo."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Unbreakable Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nezlomljiva opeka</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Unbreakable Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Nezlomljiva opeka</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Never gets destroyed unless hit by a burning or unstoppable ball, or an "
"exploding brick next to it gets hit. These bricks do not need to be "
"destroyed to win the level."
msgstr ""
"Nikoli ni uničen, razen če ga zadene goreča ali neustavljiva žoga ali če "
"zadene eksplodirajočo opeko zraven. Teh opek ni treba uničiti, da bi "
"osvojili raven."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Breakable Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zlomljiva opeka</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Breakable Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Zlomljiva opeka</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unbreakable bricks can be turned into breakable bricks using <link linkend="
"\"gift-magic-wand\">Magic Wand gift</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nezlomljive opeke lahko spremenite v lomljive opeke z uporabo <link linkend="
"\"gift-magic-wand\">darila čarobne paličice</link>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Hidden Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skrita opeka</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Hidden Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Skrita opeka</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This brick is not initially shown to the player. When hit for the first time "
"it becomes visible, and becomes a plain brick. If hit by a burning ball, or "
"an exploding brick next to it gets hit it gets destroyed as soon as it "
"appears. As long as it remains hidden it does not need to be destroyed to "
"get to the next level."
msgstr ""
"Ta opeka na začetku ni prikazana igralcu. Ob prvem udarcu postane vidna in "
"postane navadna opeka. Če jo zadene goreča žoga ali eksplozivna opeka poleg "
"nje, se uniči takoj, ko se pojavi. Dokler je skrita, ga ni treba uničiti, da "
"pridete na naslednjo stopnjo."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Multiple Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Več opek</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Multiple Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Več opek</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Needs to be hit three times before getting destroyed, unless hit by a "
"burning or unstoppable ball, or an exploding brick next to it gets destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Zadeti ga je treba trikrat, preden se ga uniči, razen če ga zadene goreča "
"ali neustavljiva žoga ali če se uniči eksplozivna opeka poleg nje."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Exploding Brick</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Eksplozivna opeka</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Exploding Brick</term>"
msgstr "<term>Eksplozivna opeka</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this brick gets hit also the bricks to the top, bottom, left and right "
"of it will get destroyed, regardless of their type."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta opeka zadeta, bodo uničene tudi opeke na vrhu, spodaj, levo in "
"desno od nje, ne glede na njihovo vrsto."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gifts"
msgstr "Darila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pictures for the gifts below are for the default theme of &kbreakout;."
msgstr "Slike za darila spodaj so za privzeto temo &kbreakout;."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gift 1000 Points"
msgstr "Darilo 1000 točk"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Score Gifts"
msgstr "Štetje daril"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If caught they award the player the number of points written on the gift."
msgstr ""
"Če ga ujamejo, igralcu dodelijo število točk, ki je napisano na darilu."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Add Life Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodaj darilo življenja</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Add Life Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Dodaj darilo življenja</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gives the player an additional life."
msgstr "Igralcu daje dodatno življenje."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Lose Life Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izgubi darilo življenja</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Lose Life Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Izgubi darilo življenja</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Makes the player lose all balls and resets the bar."
msgstr "Povzroči, da igralec izgubi vse žoge in ponastavi vrstico."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Enlarge Bar Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Povečaj darilo vrstice</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Enlarge Bar Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Povečaj darilo vrstice</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enlarges the bar."
msgstr "Poveča vrstico."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Shrink Bar Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zoži darilo vrstice</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Shrink Bar Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Zoži darilo vrstice</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shrinks the bar."
msgstr "Zoži vrstico."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Split Balls Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Razcepi darilo žogic</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Split Balls Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Razcepi darilo žogic</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Doubles the balls."
msgstr "Podvoji žogice."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Add Balls Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodaj darilo žog</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Add Balls Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Dodaj darilo žog</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gives the player an extra ball attached to the bar, which can be fired "
"whenever the player wants."
msgstr ""
"Igralcu daje dodatno žogo, pritrjeno na palico, ki jo lahko izstreli kadar "
"koli igralec želi."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Sticky Bar Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Darilo lepljiva vrstica</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Sticky Bar Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Darilo lepljiva vrstica</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After catching this gift, every time a ball touches the bar it remains "
"attached to it, allowing the player to fire again."
msgstr ""
"Potem ko ujamete to darilo, se vsakič, ko se žoga dotakne palice, ostane "
"pritrjena nanjo, kar omogoča igralcu, da znova strelja."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>More Exploding Bricks Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Darilo več eksplozivnih opek</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>More Exploding Bricks Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Darilo več eksplozivnih opek</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Makes all bricks to the top, bottom, right, and left of exploding bricks "
"exploding bricks themselves. This also applies to hidden and unbreakable "
"bricks."
msgstr ""
"Naredi vse opeke na vrhu, dnu, desno in levo iz eksplozivnih opek, ki same "
"eksplodirajo. To velja tudi za skrite in nezlomljive opeke."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Burning Ball Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Darilo goreče krogle</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Burning Ball Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Darilo goreče krogle</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Transforms all the balls into burning balls. When a burning ball hits a "
"brick also the bricks to the top, bottom, left and right of it get "
"destroyed. A burning ball destroys all types of bricks regardless of their "
"types."
msgstr ""
"Vse žoge spremeni v goreče krogle. Ko goreča krogla zadene opeko, se uničijo "
"tudi opeke na vrhu, spodaj, levo in desno od nje. Goreča krogla uniči vse "
"vrste opek, ne glede na njihovo vrsto."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Unstoppable Ball Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Darilo neustavljive žoge</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Unstoppable Ball Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Darilo neustavljive žoge</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Transforms all the balls into unstoppable balls. An unstoppable ball "
"destroys all bricks it encounters on its path, regardless of their type, and "
"never bounces against them."
msgstr ""
"Vse žoge spremeni v neustavljive žoge. Neustavljiva žoga uniči vse opeke, ki "
"jih sreča na svoji poti, ne glede na njihovo vrsto, in se nikoli ne odbije "
"od njih."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Magic Eye Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Darilo čarobno oko</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Magic Eye Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Darilo čarobno oko</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows all hidden bricks."
msgstr "Prikaže vse skrite opeke."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Magic Wand Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Darilo čarobne palice</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term id=\"gift-magic-wand\">Magic Wand Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term id=\"gift-magic-wand\">Darilo čarobne palice</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transforms all multiple and unbreakable bricks into simple bricks."
msgstr "Preoblikuje vse večkratne in nezlomljive opeke v preproste opeke."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Increase Speed Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Darilo povečanje hitrosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Increase Speed Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>Darilo povečanje hitrosti</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increases the speed of the ball by 30% of the current speed."
msgstr "Poveča hitrost žogice za 30 % trenutne hitrosti."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Decrease Speed Gift</phrase>"
