msgstr "<term>Darilo naslednje stopnje</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the next level of the game immediately."
msgstr "Takoj odpre naslednjo stopnjo igre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If possible, it is usually a good idea to send the ball above the bricks, "
"doing so you will have a smaller chance of losing the ball. Sometimes you "
"need to first make a small hole in the layer of brick to accomplish this. "
"The smaller the hole, the smaller the chance the balls comes back down."
msgstr ""
"Če je mogoče, je običajno dobro, da žogo pošljete nad zidake, saj boste tako "
"imeli manjšo možnost, da jo izgubite. Včasih morate najprej narediti majhno "
"luknjo v plasti opeke, da to dosežete. Manjša kot je luknja, manjša je "
"možnost, da se žoge vrnejo dol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When catching the add ball gift it is wise to not fire it right away but to "
"keep in instead, in case the other balls are lost. It is also advisable to "
"not catch a sticky bar gift in such a case, as doing so would force you to "
"fire all balls."
msgstr ""
"Ko ujamete darilo za dodajanje žoge, je pametno, da je ne sprožite takoj, "
"ampak jo obdržite, če se druge žoge izgubijo. Prav tako je priporočljivo, da "
"v takem primeru ne ujamete lepljivega darila, saj bi vas to prisililo, da "
"izstrelite vse žoge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When receiving a next level gift you may not want to catch it if you know "
"that there are add life gifts in the level."
msgstr ""
"Ko prejmete darilo naslednje stopnje, ga morda ne boste želeli ujeti, če "
"veste, da so na ravni dodana življenjska darila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In levels where there are a lot of hidden bricks there may be a way to win "
"the level without having to destroy most of them."
msgstr ""
"Na ravneh, kjer je veliko skritih zidakov, lahko obstaja način, kako zmagati "
"na ravni, ne da bi jih morali uničiti večino."

